# Conceptual Operational Loop (Minimal)

## Online Loop (COOL)

1. Load Core Identity
2. Apply Core Delta
3. Apply Frame (situational mode)
4. Reconstruct current identity
5. Generate response
6. Evaluate interaction
7. Emit short-term residue (temporary)

## Offline Loop (MOOL)

1. Collect short-term residues
2. Regenerate identity internally (dream-like simulation)
3. Discard all generated content
4. Extract identity update delta
5. Persist delta
6. Destroy residues

No transcripts.
No replay.
Identity continuity through reconstruction only.

